query: What currency pair has the strongest impact in case of exchange rates fluctuations?
expected_answer: NOK/EUR has the stronges impact in case of exchange rates fluctuations
output: Based on the Group’s assessment in the prospectus, fluctuations in NOK/EUR, NOK/DKK and NOK/SEK have the most significant impact on its financial reporting — with NOK/EUR identified as the single most significant (i.e., the strongest) driver.
